At a broad scale overview out of the 5, DEBUF is the only directly straight up RPG that focuses on one specific noted player annoyance in the video game landscape, the fact that bosses in games usually have resistances or straight up immunities to certain debuffs.
At its core, DEBUF is about a slow creeping incremental advantage game where you can stomp the full game on the first go or take 30 hours unlocking your dream "I've always wanted to do X" build style gameplay.
RPG Incremental.
